title: Need for Speed - ProStreet OST
description:
Hello everyone.

This is the Need For Speed: ProStreet soundtrack.

No, this is not the &#039;uncensored&#039; version of some of the songs, as this soundtrack is ripped directly from the game. All 38 tracks.

Encoded: MP3/320kbps.

Hope you enjoy. :) If you download, please seed. My computer isn&#039;t all that great and it took freakin&#039; forever to rip this.
